{"id": 2262, "genre": 1001, "title": "这些年你都是如何实践阿 Q 精神的？", "description": "你都擅长在哪些微妙的小事儿上给自己找成就感！（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 1714, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180403181535xcXn2Cz05dqHym93.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-04T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 274433, "content": "其实我们都一样，只是我还没有努力。我浪费时间，思考自己需要什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304808}, {"id": 274434, "content": "每次看点复习资料就能飞起来，因为感觉自己都懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304841}, {"id": 274180, "content": "每次堕落后，都会安慰自己下次一定能自控", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253562}, {"id": 283908, "content": "天将降大任于我必先苦我心志劳我筋骨……我一定是被选中的人\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003171}, {"id": 274182, "content": "别人不喜欢我都是因为嫉妒我。☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188634}, {"id": 274183, "content": "貌似身上没有任何一点阿Q精神～", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265441}, {"id": 274184, "content": "我好特别.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 274440, "content": "旋转跳跃，我数着钱～", "image": "img/option/option/201804052350376sPlkWp0UXaRAdS4.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221156}, {"id": 274441, "content": "凡事总要想想好的一面", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983506}, {"id": 274186, "content": "“相信自己总有一天会成功的”哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 389811}, {"id": 274187, "content": "比上不足，比下余太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303785}, {"id": 274188, "content": "跟女生走在一起，觉得自己还蛮高蛮壮的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023476}, {"id": 274189, "content": "“没事儿 我就玩一会儿手机 不影响干正事儿”", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281633}, {"id": 274190, "content": "没有什么事是比失去生命更糟糕的了。既然还活着，没有什么过不去的", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303788}, {"id": 274191, "content": "没事，还有五天就要交论文hhhhhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194738}, {"id": 274192, "content": "运动后感觉全世界都是自己的", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301455}, {"id": 274448, "content": "人生苦短，随心所愿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286491}, {"id": 274193, "content": "虽然我只有50公斤，但我感觉能一个打三个", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303804}, {"id": 277265, "content": "呃呃呃呃\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 274194, "content": "觉得只要我减肥成功就能得到我想要的一切了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195127}, {"id": 274450, "content": "每跑完一个5km，6km，都觉得自己瘦了十斤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299022}, {"id": 274195, "content": "没关系，长大了我就都会了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303811}, {"id": 274451, "content": "做完运动，感觉自己吃多了的能减回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288287}, {"id": 274196, "content": "说我不美是因为审美不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303813}, {"id": 285974, "content": "短期内做出一个非常棒的ppt", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367616}, {"id": 274199, "content": "拿自己的优势跟别人的劣势比，现在想想自己真的可笑极了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299485}, {"id": 274200, "content": "我要是做这件事肯定比他做的更好，只不过是我没兴趣而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257820}, {"id": 274456, "content": "混的不好主要是因为运气差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964934}, {"id": 274201, "content": "我是颓废派来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294729}, {"id": 274457, "content": "没女朋友是因为不想找", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964934}, {"id": 274202, "content": "心中默念\n当太阳重新升起，一切都会好起来的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303849}, {"id": 274203, "content": "每次YY自己会得到某位大牛赏识，从此迎娶白富美，走上人生巅峰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202799}, {"id": 274205, "content": "每次吃饭后都后悔 \n下次一定节省粮食", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303865}, {"id": 274206, "content": "全世界都是我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250875}, {"id": 274210, "content": "看一点书，就觉得自己能成功?", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278070}, {"id": 275751, "content": "发生了什么 都会想 这就是命吧 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315324}, {"id": 274216, "content": "照着镜子感觉自己不比吴彦祖差?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303846}, {"id": 274217, "content": "我独一无二。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298534}, {"id": 274219, "content": "看到你们的话，我感觉不是只有我一个人这么阿q", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259009}, {"id": 274475, "content": "总有一个瞬间，会忽然觉得，茫茫天地，我们不过是个匆匆行路的旅人。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304594}, {"id": 274476, "content": "来都来了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305250}, {"id": 274229, "content": "参加工作后，每年都关键时候，都被人表扬一下，然后外加一句，好好干，不会亏待你的。结果一直被亏待到现在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303968}, {"id": 274230, "content": "吼，高赞令人恐慌。\n看来自诩智商高确实是没啥卵用了。\n我怎么能现在才明白。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039682}, {"id": 274494, "content": "啊 没事反正会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305339}, {"id": 274750, "content": "每次东西坏了就不要了，但我总喜欢把它给修好摆在哪里当作自己的战利品！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1308011}, {"id": 274239, "content": "屡屡被生活当头棒喝，阿q在我身上一点点的消失", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 274495, "content": "每次努力学习时，感觉自己能上天。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021195}, {"id": 274240, "content": "这是我取得成功前所必须的磨炼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303992}, {"id": 274496, "content": "看好奇心日报而不是去学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305366}, {"id": 274241, "content": "这也不坏，还能接受。然后就没有了底线。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235373}]}